page.title: 02JANINE'S DAY
page.content: Every Wednesday I waken up at 7.30 I then stop in bed for a bit. When it's 8.00 I get dressed and look after Sabrina, my sister. At 8.35 I set off for school, I arrive about 8.45. We play out until 9.00, then we go into school. Sometimes we have assembly then we do our reading scheme work and maths. At 10.30 we go out to play until 10.45. When we come in we sometimes get on with more maths and then something we want to do. We have dinner at 12.00. After lunch we play rounders and do art. I like playing on my roller boots and with my BMX at the BMX course.
